\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9583014105128251, \"rank\": 0.0375019476685246, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his nails\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"the word\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"ICON\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"blue polish\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"his nails\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On social media, the look divided viewers, with one alleging that painted nails were meant for women.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the look\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"one alleging\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"painted nails\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Lyles said that he's not letting the criticism get to him, since he does not take the comments too seriously.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9583014105128251, \"rank\": 0.0375019476685246, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the criticism\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"the comments\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a person who knows that a lot of people have different opinions and they have them for different reasons,\\\" he toldUS Weekly.\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"different opinions\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"different reasons\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest, I am so confident in myself that it does not really matter.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's funny at times.\\\"\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He acknowledged that while he has an understanding for a difference in opinions, he finds amusement in how people on social media get so upset over some decisions he makes.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an understanding\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"opinions\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"amusement\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"some decisions\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes, it's like: 'Hey, I know you were brought up this way, but I was brought up that way,' and the fact that you can not see the differences of why I might do it, I find that entertaining,\\\" he continued.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the differences\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know, peoplelikeme because I do this.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just being myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The US sprinter also spoke candidly about his personality, and how sometimes he's perceived in a negative light because of his confidence.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1883, \"end\": 1885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9929396313192915, \"rank\": 0.0065557524969652985, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his personality\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"a negative light\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"his confidence\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The most misunderstood thing is the balance between cocky and confident,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most misunderstood thing\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a strong line that people assume my confidence is cockiness.\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strong line\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"my confidence\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will say this.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anybody who thought I was cocky and met me, they are instantly like: 'Oh, that's the nicest, coolest guy I have ever met in my life.'\\\"\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nicest, coolest guy\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He further described how people's opinions of him change once they get to know him.\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people's opinions\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never blame anybody who thinks that I am cocky.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a 'you have not met me situation.'\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"situation\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's all,\\\" he concluded.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics is not Lyles' first time showcasing his painted nails.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2567, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9583014105128251, \"rank\": 0.0375019476685246, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"his painted nails\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the New Balance Indoor Grand Prix in February, he had his nails painted red and black, and also shared a photo of his hands over his face after competing in the event on social media.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISU_Grand_Prix_of_Figure_Skating\", \"score\": 0.988769464653553, \"rank\": 0.008995238825775754, \"text\": \"Grand Prix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISU_Grand_Prix_of_Figure_Skating\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ISU_Grand_Prix_of_Figure_Skating\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"his nails\", \"from\": 2672,